</div>I'm not sure he cares about quality, given that this year's <a href="http://monsterhunternation.com/2015/02/02/sad-puppies-3-the-slatening/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Sad Puppy list</a> includes the talentless Kevin Anderson. I don't care if he shares all my beliefs (at the very least, we have similar tastes in rock music, given that we're both big fans of Rush), Kevin Anderson is a SHITTY, HORRIBLE, SUCKY, AWFUL writer.
						</blockquote>
					</div>

					
				</div>
			</div>
			
