		</div>
	</div>
</div>The whole purpose of art is to comment on the human experience. By definition art is entwined with politics, because politics are a consequence of the human experience.<br />
<br />
You cannot judge a work of art in a vacuum. Without personal experience you have no tools to judge it with.
